name: tram production | tram | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/4093/documentation

The dataset represents the production of one tram. Disposal of tram is included. 

The activity starts with the material (steel, aluminium, copper, polyethylene, rubber, glass and paint) for the production of the tram.

The activity ends with the production of one tram and its disposal. The activity includes the material consumption for the production (steel, aluminium, copper, rubber, glass and paint), the energy consumption (electricity and light fuel oil) and until and including the consumption of lead (battery).
category: C:Manufacturing/30:Manufacture of other transport equipment/302:Manufacture of railway locomotives and rolling stock/3020:Manufacture of railway locomotives and rolling stock

processDocumentation.geographyDescription: Vehicle manufacturing data are taken from one production site in  Switzerland.
processDocumentation.technologyDescription: The material composition of a tram is obtained from Maibach et al. (1999). Manufacturing expenditures and interventions for a tram are obtained from Maibach et al. (1999). However, is assumed that 50% of the heating energy is based on natural gas and 50% is based on light fuel oil. ;References:;Maibach M., Peter D. and Seiler B. (1999) Ökoinventar Transporte: Grundlagen für den ökologischen Vergleich von Transportsystemen und den Einbezug von Transportsystemen in Ökobilanzen. Technischer Schlussbericht. In: Schweizerischer Nationalfonds zur Förderung der wissenschaftlichen Forschung (ed. SPP Umwelt M.). 2nd Edition. INFRAS, Zürich
processDocumentation.dataTreatmentDescription: Data from one production site in Switzerland is used as an first estimate for Europe
